{"word":"εὐφημέω","slug":"εὐφημέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n45402\" key=\"eu)fhme/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">εὐφημ-έω</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dor.\">Dor.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">εὐφᾱμέω</orth>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">εὔφημος</etym>) <sense id=\"n45402.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">use words of good omen</tr_>, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δυσφημέω</foreign>: </sense> <sense n=\"I\" id=\"n45402.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">avoid all unlucky words</tr_>, during sacred rites: hence, as the surest mode of avoiding them, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">keep a religious silence</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φέρτε δὲ χερσὶν ὕδωρ εὐφημῆσαί τε κέλεσθε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:171\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.171</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0533.tlg002:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Call.\">Call.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ap.\">Ap.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0533.tlg002:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; mostly imper., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εὐφήμει, εὐφημεῖτε</foreign>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">hush! be still</tr_>! <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0